      <title>习近平如何在六大会议上做出大动作震惊世界</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/how-xi-can-shock-the-world-with-big-bang-moves-at-china-plenum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国有能力在一次高风险的政策会议上结束房地产危机，包括采取“一揽子解决方案”，即像美联储那样注入资金。但它不太可能立即采取行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/how-xi-can-shock-the-world-with-big-bang-moves-at-china-plenum</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据 Axios 报道，舒默愿意取代拜登成为提名人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/schumer-open-to-replacing-biden-as-nominee-axios-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 Axios 报道，由于对总统的精神敏锐度和赢得连任的能力存在担忧，参议院多数党领袖查克·舒默愿意取代乔·拜登成为民主党候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/schumer-open-to-replacing-biden-as-nominee-axios-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 22:13:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙向乌克兰派遣培训师的计划在选举后受阻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/macron-s-plan-to-send-trainers-to-ukraine-falters-after-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙在向乌克兰派遣军事教练的提议中的主要合作伙伴对该提议的前景表示怀疑，因为最近的选举让这位法国总统的势力减弱了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/macron-s-plan-to-send-trainers-to-ukraine-falters-after-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 22:00:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默称“令人震惊”的监狱是英国最紧迫的危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/starmer-says-shocking-prisons-are-the-uk-s-most-urgent-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默表示，解决英国监狱过度拥挤危机是他的主要国内任务，并表示里希·苏纳克领导的保守党留下的公共服务“状况糟糕”，这意味着不受欢迎的决定不可避免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/starmer-says-shocking-prisons-are-the-uk-s-most-urgent-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大计划购买潜艇，距离北约防御目标更近一步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/canada-plans-to-buy-submarines-inching-closer-to-nato-defense-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多试图平息盟友的批评，该国表示将开始购买潜艇舰队，此举可能会增加其国防开支，以满足北约的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/canada-plans-to-buy-submarines-inching-closer-to-nato-defense-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 20:36:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
