    <item>
      <title>纽约副州长敦促拜登停止竞选连任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/new-york-s-lieutenant-governor-urges-biden-to-end-reelection-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州副州长安东尼奥·德尔加多是该州最杰出的民主党人之一，他于周三呼吁乔·拜登下台，成为最新一位呼吁总统结束连任竞选的民选官员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/new-york-s-lieutenant-governor-urges-biden-to-end-reelection-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 19:55:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>律师称梅内德斯的妻子隐瞒了有关奔驰的真相</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/menendez-lawyer-says-wife-hid-truth-about-car-given-by-felon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参议员鲍勃·梅嫩德斯的律师告诉陪审员，这位政客的妻子没有告诉他如何从一名被定罪的重罪犯那里得到一辆奔驰车，而这名重罪犯在该议员的腐败审判期间作证称，这辆车是贿赂所得。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/menendez-lawyer-says-wife-hid-truth-about-car-given-by-felon</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 17:34:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北约将谴责中国在乌克兰问题上支持俄罗斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/nato-set-to-call-out-china-over-support-for-russia-s-war-machine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，北约领导人将以北约史上最强硬的言辞，谴责中国对俄罗斯的军事支持，有迹象表明北京方面正在为与乌克兰的冲突研发攻击无人机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/nato-set-to-call-out-china-over-support-for-russia-s-war-machine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:44:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登支持者和筹款人乔治克鲁尼要求总统放弃竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-10/urgent-actor-george-clooney-a-high-profile-biden-supporter-and-fundraiser-asks-president-to-leave-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[他在《纽约时报》的一篇评论文章中写道，他喜欢拜登，但如果他成为候选人，共和党将输掉总统竞选，并失去在国会的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-10/urgent-actor-george-clooney-a-high-profile-biden-supporter-and-fundraiser-asks-president-to-leave-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:23:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
